OL,3,CLong queues and expensive shops make
OL,4,CManchester airport UK's worst
OL,6,FManchester has been ranked the worst
OL,7,Fairport in the UK for the third year
OL,8,Fin a row, with passengers complaining
OL,9,Fof queues, lack of seating and
OL,10,Fexpensive shops and restaurants.
OL,12,FTerminal 3 finished bottom of the
OL,13,Fstudy for the third year running while
OL,14,FLiverpool John Lennon airport came out
OL,15,Fon top.
OL,17,FThe UK consumer watchdog Which?
OL,18,Frevealed the ranking in its annual
OL,19,Fairport survey where they spoke to
OL,20,F7,000 people about their experiences
OL,21,Fin the last 12 months.
