OL,3,CLong queues and expensive shops make
OL,4,CManchester airport UK's worst
OL,6,FAirports were rated in 11 categories
OL,7,Fincluding seating, staff, toilets and
OL,8,Fqueues at check in, bag drop, passport
OL,9,Fcontrol and security.
OL,11,FOne traveller told Which? their
OL,12,Fexperience at Manchester Airport was
OL,13,F"just awful", adding: "The worst
OL,14,Fadvert for anyone flying to the UK.
OL,15,FIt's the worst airport I have ever
OL,16,Fused."
