OL,3,CLong queues and expensive shops make
OL,4,CManchester airport UK's worst
OL,6,FTerminal 1, which is scheduled for
OL,7,Fclosure next year, fared only
OL,8,Fmarginally better, with a customer
OL,9,Fscore of 40 per cent and came second
OL,10,Fbottom of the league.
OL,12,FManchester, the UK's third-biggest
OL,13,Fairport, received just one star for
OL,14,Fits staff, queues at security and
OL,15,Fprices in shops, and two star ratings
OL,16,Fin most of the remaining categories.
OL,18,FIts highest rating of three stars was
OL,19,Ffor its toilets.
