OL,3,CLong queues and expensive shops make
OL,4,CManchester airport UK's worst
OL,6,FTerminal 2, which has undergone a huge
OL,7,Fupgrade, was the highest rated of
OL,8,FManchester's Terminals, tied with
OL,9,FHeathrow Terminal 4 with a score of 51
OL,10,Fper cent.
OL,12,FBut it still came 6th bottom in a
OL,13,Fleague of 29 airport terminals across
OL,14,Fthe country.
OL,16,FManchester Airport bosses have hit
OL,17,Fback, branding the survey's findings
OL,18,Fas "outdated and unrepresentative".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
