OL,3,CLong queues and expensive shops make
OL,4,CManchester airport UK's worst
OL,6,FThey say the survey placed no value on
OL,7,Fthe range of destinations offered or
OL,8,Fchoice of airlines, nor did it rate
OL,9,Fthe service to disabled passengers.
OL,11,FA Manchester Airport spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "As in previous years, Which? is
OL,13,Fletting consumers down with over-
OL,14,Fsimplified judgements based on the
OL,15,Foutdated and unrepresentative
OL,16,Ftestimony of a narrow group of
OL,17,Ftravellers, as well as publishing
OL,18,Fmisleading statements and factual
OL,19,Finaccuracies.
